Dialogue: 0,00:00:00.000,00:00:06.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go to system of conservation laws.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:06.000,00:00:16.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,Find a volume and actually also find a difference are not very difficult with not just one conservation law but a system of conservation laws.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:16.000,00:00:26.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,A system of conservation law is going to be multiple quantities coupled with each other.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:26.000,00:00:43.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,In a conservation law sense, that means the flux of one quantity is determined not just as a function of that quantity itself but as a multivariate function of several quantities.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:43.000,00:00:53.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,The simplest type of conservation law is coupling two quantities.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:53.000,00:00:55.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So the time derivative of...
Dialogue: 0,00:00:55.000,00:00:56.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,Let me...
Dialogue: 0,00:00:56.000,00:00:58.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,Let me illustrate it in a scalar sense.
Dialogue: 0,00:00:58.000,00:01:11.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,The time derivative of u1 plus a flux, I call it 1, of u1 and u2 dx is equal to 0.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:11.000,00:01:23.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,Also, the time derivative of u2 is a function also of u1 and u2.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:23.000,00:01:25.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,If f1 and f2 are both 0,
Dialogue: 0,00:01:25.000,00:01:26.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,f1 and f2 are both 0,
Dialogue: 0,00:01:26.000,00:01:34.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,if f1 and f2 are both linear, then this is not very different from the second project we just submitted last week.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:34.000,00:01:41.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,But in this case, f1 and f2 can be nonlinear functions.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:41.000,00:01:43.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So I'm just going to give very...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:43.000,00:01:47.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,I'm just going to give one example that is exactly like that.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:47.000,00:01:50.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,It's called the shallow water equation.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:50.000,00:01:51.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,It's called the shallow water equation.
Dialogue: 0,00:01:51.000,00:01:53.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,It's called the shallow water equation.
