Dialogue: 0,00:04:18.000,00:04:20.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,The momentum, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:20.000,00:04:26.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,So these are the two conservative quantities in this equation.
